data.description: Under $300K!!! Check out this lovely home sitting in a well established neighborhood on a huge lot for plenty of backyard fun!! The primary bedroom is on the main level with 3 bedrooms upstairs. You will be surprised how open and spacious the eat-in kitchen. This house has fresh paint and brand new carpet throughout. All HVAC ductwork is new!!! More lot beyond the fence, almost double! The large 2 car garage is spacious enough for those hobbies and storage! Not many large lots like this out there, plenty of space for the RV's, boats and trailers! Schedule your showing today!
